# swaypaper

Simple terminal wallpaper picker for wlroots compositors.

Supports:

- Niri
- Hyprland
- Sway
- i3

Browse wallpapers with arrow keys and apply them instantly with `swaybg`.

Can automatically add wallpaper startup lines to your compositor config so wallpapers persist after relogin.

Default wallpaper directory:

```text
~/Pictures/Wallpapers
```

Supported formats:

- jpg
- jpeg
- png
- webp
